dth: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Frecuencia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Baja&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Usuario en módulo de proveedores.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:38.25pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El sistema despliega el formulario, el usuario ingresa RUT, nombre, email y teléfono [Excepción 1], el sistema valida la unicidad del RUT [Excepción 2], el sistema guarda al nuevo proveedor y muestra una confirmacion de éxito, al usuario.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:45.94824218749999pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: Formato de email inválido. El sistema solicita corregir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 2: RUT ya existe. El sistema notifica la duplicidad.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El proveedor queda disponible para asociaciones comerciales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; ver